    <item>
      <title>Revolut 称元平台是金融诈骗的“温床”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/meta-platforms-are-hotbed-for-financial-scams-revolut-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，向英国金融应用程序 Revolut Ltd. 举报的大多数诈骗都是在 Meta Platforms Inc. 社交媒体上开始的，其中大部分资金都输给了“快速致富”的投资计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/meta-platforms-are-hotbed-for-financial-scams-revolut-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 11:57:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adyen 销售业绩好转，重新赢得投资者信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/adyen-s-net-revenue-beats-estimates-as-customer-spending-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者支出增加，支付处理公司 Adyen NV 下半年净收入超出预期，该公司股价飙升，这表明该公司正在重新赢得投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/adyen-s-net-revenue-beats-estimates-as-customer-spending-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 06:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Arm首席执行官表示人工智能热潮在创纪录的反弹后才刚刚开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/arm-gives-bullish-forecast-makes-headway-pushing-into-new-areas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人工智能支出帮助增强芯片设计商的预测后，Arm Holdings Plc 股价周四飙升 64%。该公司首席执行官表示，人工智能带来的巨大机遇仍处于早期阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/arm-gives-bullish-forecast-makes-headway-pushing-into-new-areas</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
